1. Trump signed the GENIUS Act, and the first federal regulatory framework for stablecoins in the United States was implemented;
2. Chairman of the US SEC: Stablecoins belong to the scope of banking regulators;
3. Ethereum's market value exceeds Costco, and its global asset market value ranking rises to 29th;
4. SharpLink Gaming increased its holdings by another 19,084 ETH;
5. WLFI spent $200,000 to purchase BANK, TAG, EGL1, LIBERTY, and B;
6. Ether.fi will launch the HyperLiquid ecosystem and launch beHYPE pledge tokens;
7. Trump seeks to impose a minimum tariff of 15-20% on all EU goods;
8. Fed Governor Waller: If the Fed waits another six weeks to cut interest rates, it may not be a big problem, but there is no reason to continue to delay;
9. Bank of America: The trade war hits the "American exceptionalism", and the proportion of global funds in US stocks has dropped sharply;
10. Basel Medical Group has suspended its Bitcoin acquisition strategy;
11. Analysis: GENIUS The bill bans yield-based stablecoins, which will benefit Ethereum DeFi;
12. Report: Crypto theft losses are expected to reach $4 billion in 2025, wallet attacks have surged, and robberies have also increased significantly;
13. James Wynn: BTC.D rebounds, and the alt season may be suspended;
14. Bit Digital increased its holdings by 19,683 ETH, and its total holdings rose to more than 120,000 ETH;
15. Two related wallets transferred 2,831 MKR to Binance, making a profit of $1.58 million;
16. Cumberland transferred 35,000 Ethereum to Coinbase, worth about $126 million;
17. Trend Research address withdrew another 1.0045 million UNI from Binance, worth more than $10.69 million;
18. Listed company MEI Pharm established an LTC treasury, which will invest more than $100 million, and the founder of LTC will join the board of directors;
19. TAO Synergies, a US-listed company, spent $10 million to purchase TAO tokens as a treasury asset reserve;
20. dYdX acquired the encrypted social trading platform Pocket Protector, which was its first external acquisition;
21. BIYA, a Nasdaq-listed company, plans to acquire Starfish, the parent company of UpTop.Meme, to enter Web3 and expects to increase profits by $15 million;
22. The initial value of the US one-year inflation rate in July is 4.4%, the expected value is 5.00%, and the previous value is 5.00%;
23. American Express CEO: Stablecoins are more like an investment tool and will not replace legal tender;
24. JD Coin Chain Technology: JD Stablecoin has not been issued, and all trading platforms JD-HKD/USD are counterfeit;
25. Binance: The additional Gas fees incurred by some users during the Bonding Curve TGE have been returned;
26. Musk posted Ani-related tweets again, and the market value of the Meme coin Ani with the same name broke through in a short time $44 million.
